            "whatAreTheIntendedOutcomesOfTheProject": "The project intends to: (1) Create a minimum of 25 full-time skilled positions for local residents; (2) Establish compliant and environmentally responsible extraction operations; (3) Contribute to the local tax base, supporting municipal services; (4) Develop partnerships with Indigenous communities and local suppliers; and (5) Deliver measurable reductions in operational emissions through modern equipment and practices.",
